{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-archive-js","path":"/archive/","result":{"data":{"posts":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"ba7a842e-8327-540f-b5f5-37bc97f27b86","publishedAt":"2020-08-17T03:00:00.000Z","mainImage":{"crop":null,"hotspot":null,"asset":{"_id":"image-1f3be06cf239b485c7a7e78dc937e22484d220be-640x480-png"},"alt":"min-wen-chun-qiu"},"title":"反封建专制里程碑：邓小平“八一八”讲话","_rawExcerpt":[{"_key":"8243b3e79acb","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"8243b3e79acb0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"25年前的8月18日，邓小平在政治局扩大会议上作了一个意义重大的讲话：《党和国家领导制度的改革》。在这个重要讲话中，邓小平分析了我们党和国家领导制度的种种弊端，如：官僚主义现象，突出表现为高高在上、滥用权力、脱离实际、脱离群众、思想僵化、墨守成规、不负责任、不守信用、压制民主、欺上瞒下、专横跋扈、贪赃枉法等等；"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"slug":{"current":"fan-feng-jian-dxp-81"}}},{"node":{"id":"dab23e8e-f924-56f9-911b-0a1b0d5a4af9","publishedAt":"2020-07-05T03:00:00.000Z","mainImage":{"crop":null,"hotspot":null,"asset":{"_id":"image-1f3be06cf239b485c7a7e78dc937e22484d220be-640x480-png"},"alt":"国史札记"},"title":"评《国史札记》兼论高饶事件","_rawExcerpt":[{"_key":"54417e8a0d42","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"54417e8a0d420","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"林蕴晖教授的著作《国史札记·事件篇》，大量利用了近年来公布的新史料，以新的史观方法，钩沉梳理了建国以来党史上的一系列重大事件，以个人的独立研究，剔抉发微，廓清了一些历史之谜，于历史研究中给人们以现实的思考，可称为是中国当代史研究中不断推陈出新的扛鼎之作。阅读该书，可对学界的中国当代史梳理工作一窥端倪。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"slug":{"current":"guo-shi-zha-ji"}}},{"node":{"id":"7bcc8d09-6809-512b-9d50-27aa83e9bc96","publishedAt":"2019-04-08T22:00:00.000Z","mainImage":{"crop":{"_key":null,"_type":"sanity.imageCrop","top":0.42778306115423054,"bottom":0,"left":0.04426787741203178,"right":0.5039727582292847},"hotspot":{"_key":null,"_type":"sanity.imageHotspot","x":0.2701475595913736,"y":0.7138915305771152,"height":0.5722169388457694,"width":0.4517593643586836},"asset":{"_id":"image-26310230bf276b6456ba36e2e232a9c7ae154b8e-1350x900-png"},"alt":"Person standing in a field of sunflowers"},"title":"Exploration powered by structured content","_rawExcerpt":[{"_key":"bdfbfa656915","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"bdfbf